data.description:
Centrally located between I-35, I-240, & I-40, and about a mile west of Tinker Air Force Base, this brick 3-bed 1.5-bath home offers convenient access to a lot of OKC/Midwest City/Del City. French doors with built-in blinds; tiled shower; stone kitchen counters; tiled floors in kitchen, bathrooms, and entry; 2-car attached garage; fenced back yard. Contact me today to schedule your personal tour of the home! Seller is offering $3,000 concessions to the buyer at closing for carpet and painting.
*Must close at Chicago title in Midwest City.
